{"tid":689752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最美候選人！墨西哥18歲正妹選市長","createTime":"2018-06-04T09:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T09:18:39.000Z","uid":153228,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b88f27ee0c023996e61ef14b273108080deefa1d","tid":689752,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2446179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2446179&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1DQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=82f2c56c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2446179&h=348c1892\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2446179</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpO1HAcS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpO1HAcS.jpg&h=09d169c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶拉表示：「我因為缺乏經驗而備受質疑，但我認為，市長必須具備領導才能、誠實守信，這比政治經驗還更重要。」（圖擷自twitter）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php4Bklus.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php4Bklus.jpg&h=8449c1f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕墨西哥即將在7月1日舉行大選，除了總統，地方政府也將選出首長，其中特帕蒂特蘭市（Tepatitl&aacute;n）的一位市長候選人年僅18歲，是墨西哥歷史上最年輕的公職參選人，她精通多門外語，備受矚目。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，去年9月才剛滿18歲的寶拉（Paola Gonz&aacute;lez）出來競選墨西哥的特帕蒂特蘭市市長，寶拉的父親是當地綠黨的黨主席，她自述自己從13歲開始就接觸政治，踏入NGO做志工，15歲就成立了自己的基金會，名為「獻出一個微笑當做禮物」（Regala una sonrisa），致力於幫助那些有需要的人。<br />\n<br />\n寶拉顏值高，精通多門外語，除了母語西班牙語外，她還精通英語、法語、葡萄牙語，甚至還會說一些羅馬尼亞語和加泰羅尼亞語。<br />\n<br />\n由於寶拉年僅18歲，外界質疑其缺乏政治經驗，對此寶拉回應：「我因為缺乏經驗而備受質疑，但我認為，市長必須具備領導才能、誠實守信，這比政治經驗還更重要。」她同時強調：「我也沒有偷竊和貪腐的經歷。」<br />\n<br />\n對於為何要參選市長，寶拉說表示，政治官員們稱在特帕蒂特蘭市，年輕人占到總人口的54%，她如果出面參選，勢必能獲取年輕選民的支持，在政治官員極力勸說下，她決定出馬參選。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpKqvm2g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpKqvm2g.jpg&h=b2d83f58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶拉與墨西哥總統候選人奧布拉多爾（Andr&eacute;s Manuel L&oacute;pez Obrador）。（圖擷自twitter）"},{"pid":"0915679a32c9ad3e7efe1f4a87478610ed8a0aa9","tid":689752,"uid":153228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:56:32.000Z","msg":"墨西哥<br />\nmolamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65c2dde16549ec183df5d778d6ccbbdf89041fb","tid":689752,"uid":123264,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0915679a32c9ad3e7efe1f4a87478610ed8a0aa9","tid":689752,"uid":153228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:56:32.000Z","msg":"墨西哥<br />\nmolamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個西神早比毒犯大佬屌到爛"},{"pid":"096acae9b23a9929bdca223f7d985900a8ec11cf","tid":689752,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"d65c2dde16549ec183df5d778d6ccbbdf89041fb","tid":689752,"uid":123264,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0915679a32c9ad3e7efe1f4a87478610ed8a0aa9","tid":689752,"uid":153228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:56:32.000Z","msg":"墨西哥<br />\nmolamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個西神早比毒犯大佬屌到爛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"佢老豆係大粒野，邊洗俾人屌<img src=\"/assets/face